movies.title: Saw
movies.summary: Two strangers awaken in a room with no recollection of how they got there, and soon discover they're pawns in a deadly game perpetrated by a notorious serial killer.

movies.title: Up
movies.summary: 78-year-old Carl Fredricksen travels to Paradise Falls in his house equipped with balloons, inadvertently taking a young stowaway.

movies.title: Step Up 2: The Streets
movies.summary: Romantic sparks occur between two dance students from different backgrounds at the Maryland School of the Arts.

movies.title: Null
movies.summary: The character in this surrealist short film takes a medicine called "Null" that has very existential adverse effects.

movies.title: Solitary
movies.summary: 'Solitary' is a contained sci-fi film about a man who wakes up inside a room to discover he's a prisoner sent into space to form Earth's first colony, and worse - his cell mate Alana is hell bent on destroying everything.

movies.title: Archive
movies.summary: 2038: George Almore is working on a true human-equivalent AI. His latest prototype is almost ready. This sensitive phase is also the riskiest. Especially as he has a goal that must be hidden at all costs.

movies.title: Monsters
movies.summary: Six years after Earth has suffered an alien invasion, a cynical journalist agrees to escort a shaken American tourist through an infected zone in Mexico to the safety of the U.S. border.

movies.title: Madhouse
movies.summary: A young psychiatric intern unearths secrets about the mental health facility in which he works.
